name: Health Seller
description:
Made for mini Jam 128 with the theme Health

A simple clicker game where you start off making some health pills to sell and grow from there.  Your net worth is always going up and never can go down so your profits are as high as the end of the universe well sorta.

Controls 

Mouse to click and move around menus

Holding Down these keys

Left shift - Hire / assign 50 workers

CTRL - Hire/ assign 10  workers

CTRL + Left Shift - Hire/Assign 500 workers

Right Shift - Hire/Assign 1000 workers
